The paper discusses differentially private methods for publishing histograms, which is a topic related to privacy and data management. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves optimization and evaluation of different methods, which falls under the categories of cs.DB (Databases) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses real datasets and performs experiments, which are common in the categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
